      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver passes NAFEMS benchmark suite and internal patch tests for linear elastic and contact problems representative of pedicle screw mechanics.",
      "rationale": "NAFEMS LE1 and LE10 benchmarks reproduced within 0.5% error. Contact formulation verified against Hertzian contact analytical solution. Numerical code verification is adequate for Gradation 2 per project requirements."
