      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities replicate the COU geometry, loading mode, and boundary conditions; validation domain encompasses the intended use domain.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the exact non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw geometry intended for submission, under ASTM F1717 compression-bending loading that directly represents the clinical bending loads on posterior spinal instrumentation. Two-laboratory validation strengthens generalizability. Validation domain is coincident with COU domain for geometry and loading mode. Gradation 3 achieved."
    }
